Packages 
Package Description
application_frames
Contains the frames used to make up the interface of the entire application, including the main application frame, the Settings window and the Attribute Table window.
core_classes
Contains definitions of the atomic elements used to make up the functionality of the application, including Features and Layers.
core_components
Contains the core components of the application
custom_components
Contains the custom components of the application
database
Contains the class for the database connection
effects
Contains the effects of the application
features
Contains the classes for the feature geometries
models
Contains the classes for the models
renderers
Contains the classes for rendering features
tester
This package is only for testing
toolset
Contains the tools for the application
